#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Point of "
"Sale app </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: "
"normal;\">h</span></font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                andles in-store sales of bouquets, flowers, gift cards, and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">POS-app </"
"font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"></"
"span></font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                håndterer salg af buketter, blomster, gavekort og meget mere "
"i butikken."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Sales app "
"</font>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">makes it simple to handle customer orders, including big "
"floral arrangements for weddings, corporate events, and other special "
"occasions.</span></font>\n"
"                </strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"                    <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Salgsappen </"
"font>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-"
"weight: normal;\">forenkler håndteringen af kundeordrer, inklusive store "
"blomsterarrangementer til bryllupper, firmafester og andre særlige "
"begivenheder.</span></font>\n"
"                </strong>"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The CRM app</font></"
"strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> helps you manage customer "
"relationships, event requests, and flower inquiries easily.</font><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">CRM-appen</font></"
"strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> hjælper dig med nemt at håndtere "
"kunderelationer samt event- og blomsterforespørgsler.</font><br/>"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Purchase app</font></"
"strong> manages vendor and ensures your shop is stocked with the freshest "
"flowers."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Indkøbsappen</font></"
"strong> håndterer leverandører og sikrer, at din butik altid har de "
"friskeste blomster på lager."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">The Website app </font></"
"strong>allows customers to showcase your flowers vision and services online."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Hjemmesideappen </font></"
"strong>gør det muligt for kunder at fremvise deres blomsterarrangementer og "
"serviceydelser online."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.contactus
msgid ""
"<strong><strong><i class=\"fa fa-phone fa-fw\"/></strong></strong>&amp;nbsp;"
"+44 1223 123456"
msgstr ""
"<strong><strong><i class=\"fa fa-phone fa-fw\"/></strong></strong>&amp;nbsp;"
"+44 1223 123456"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Activate payment methods: </strong>Activate payment options such as "
"Cash, Card, Mobile Payments, and Gift Cards directly in your POS settings."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aktivér betalingsformer: </strong>Aktivér betalingsmuligheder som "
"kontant, kort, mobile betalinger og gavekort direkte i dine POS-"
"indstillinger."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Basics</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Det grundlæggende</strong>"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Choose the best deal</strong>: Pick the vendor offering the best "
"deal for the requested materials."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Vælg det bedste tilbud</strong>: Vælg den leverandør, som giver dig "
"det bedste tilbud for de anmodede materialer."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create a Purchase Order</strong>: Order the flowers, plants, and "
"accessories you need for your business."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opret en indkøbsordre</strong>: Bestil de blomster, planter og det "
"tilbehør, som du har brug for."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create tailored sales quotations: </strong>Generate a customized "
"Sales Quotation for weddings, birthdays, or corporate floral events, "
"directly on the sales app."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opret skræddersyede salgstilbud: </strong>Generér et tilpasset "
"salgstilbud til bryllupper, fødselsdage eller firmaarrangementer direkte i "
"salgsappen."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Extend your offerings: </strong>Configure Gift Cards to offer "
"flexible floral gifts and provide more options for your clients."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Udvid dit tilbud: </strong>Konfigurér gavekort til fleksible "
"blomstergaver, så dine kunder får flere valgmuligheder."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Manage customer requests</strong>: Track customer inquiries coming "
"from your Website (such as wedding floral requests or custom bouquet "
"orders), manage engagement, follow up easily, and convert them into "
"confirmed sales\n"
"            opportunities."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Håndtér kundeforespørgsler</strong>: Spor kundeforespørgsler fra din "
"hjemmeside (blomsterarrangementer til bryllupper eller bestillinger på "
"personlige buketter), håndtér engagement, følg nemt op, og konvertér dem til "
"bekræftede\n"
"            salg."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Organize event projects: </strong>Create a project to manage and "
"organize specific events, assign tasks, set deadlines, and track progress."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Organisér eventprojekter: </strong>Opret et projekt til håndtering "
"og organisering af bestemte arrangementer, tildel opgaver, sæt deadlines, og "
"spor fremskridt."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Set up product offering: </strong>Create and configure your flower "
"products and add variants if you have different size or color for the same "
"product. You can also add an extra charges for specific options (e.g., +£2 "
"for a\n"
"            red tulip, +£10 for a medium bouquet)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Opsæt produktudbud: </strong>Opret og konfigurér dine "
"blomsterprodukter, og tilføj varianter, hvis produkterne findes i "
"forskellige størrelser eller farver. Du kan også tilføje ekstra gebyrer for "
"bestemte muligheder (fx +2 kr. for en rød tulipan, +10 kr. for en mellemstor "
"buket)."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Showcase your floral vision and offer: </strong>Configure your "
"website to highlight your floral style, present your services and get new "
"opportunities through a contact form."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Præsentér dine blomsterarrangementer og tilbud: </strong>Konfigurér "
"din hjemmeside for at fremhæve din blomsterstil, præsentere dine "
"serviceydelser, og få nye salg via en kontaktformular."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Take orders in Point of Sale</strong>: Open a register and process "
"in-store purchases such as bouquets, flowers, cards, and more."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Tag imod ordrer i POS</strong>: Åbn en kasse, og håndtér køb i "
"butikken, f.eks. buketter, blomster, kort og meget mere."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Use Case</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Brugsscenarie</strong>"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>You didn't import demo data?</strong> You can still do it. Go to "
"<strong>Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Florist Package</strong> and "
"check the related box."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu?</strong> Du kan stadig nå "
"det. Gå til <strong>Apps &gt; Brancher &gt; Opgradér din pakke til "
"blomsterhandlere</strong>, og markér det relevante felt."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the <strong>eCommerce </strong>features to extend your floral business."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj <strong>e-Handelsfunktioner </strong>til udvidelse af din "
"blomsterforretning."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add<strong> product categories</strong> to organize your point of sales and "
"make your products easier to find during busy periods. (e.g. Bouquets, "
"Flowers, Plants, Other,...)"
msgstr ""
"Tilføj<strong> produktkategorier</strong> for at organisere dit kassesystem, "
"så dine produkter er nemmere at finde i travle perioder (f.eks. buketter, "
"blomster, planter m.m.)"

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Also, create beautiful <strong>Quotation Templates</strong> for specific "
"requests like wedding floral packages, making it faster and easier to send "
"offers to clients."
msgstr ""
"Du kan også oprette smukke <strong>tilbudsskabeloner</strong> til bestemte "
"forespørgsler, såsom blomster til bryllupper, så det er nemmere og hurtigere "
"at sende tilbud til kunder."

#. module: florist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:florist.welcome_article_body
msgid "Because: we can buy ourselves flowers! 💐"
msgstr "Fordi vi kan købe blomster til os selv! 💐"

